# A Cassette Tape Culture (Phase One)

A Cassette Tape Culture (Phase One) is the second recording by American industrial band ATelecine, released in 2010 through Pendu Sound Recordings in a limited edition of 500 copies.
Track listing
Side Y
# "Find Nothing Else"
# "Chroeg Xen"
# "It's All Write"
# "She Is Beautiful"
# "Kitchen Light"
# "A Cassette Played"
Side Z
# "Auon" (live ver)
# "Some What Daft"
# "Elijah's New Sun"
# "I Came I Sat I Departed"
# "RH"
# "Never Was a Dreamer"
